          // Article Content Section
          section#article-content.mb-5

            // Introduction Alert
            .alert.alert-info.mb-4
              p.mb-0
                i.bi.bi-info-circle.me-2
                strong What you'll learn:
                | How to understand the complexity of measuring AI contribution to code, why traditional metrics fail, and practical frameworks for tracking AI's impact on development productivity.

