                      i.bi.bi-graph-up-arrow.me-2
                      | Code Complexity Analysis
                  .accordion-collapse.collapse#collapseComplexity(
                    aria-labelledby='headingComplexity'
                    data-bs-parent='#enterpriseAccordion'
                  )
                    .accordion-body
                      p.
                        AI-generated code often has different complexity patterns than human code. Static analysis might reveal these signatures.

